00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:49.650
kind of huge body of health research that's
out there. When you think about the first

00:21:49.650 --> 00:21:53.099
slide I showed, that cacophony of information
that we get, one reason that that doesn't

00:21:53.099 --> 00:21:57.549
work is because it doesn't have relevance
to us, right? It's all generic, impersonal

00:21:57.549 --> 00:22:07.169
data. You know, if a study says that 50 percent
