00:23:11.849 --> 00:23:20.470
information becomes very, very compelling
and relevant to us in explicit terms. So there

00:23:20.470 --> 00:23:26.340
are all sorts of examples of this. The--,
kind of--, since I started writing the book

00:23:26.340 --> 00:23:31.690
two years ago, this was very scattershot.
There were a few tools here or there. In fact

00:23:31.690 --> 00:23:35.490
when I started work on the book, things like
