00:38:20.519 --> 00:38:27.680
So my experience has indicated that even people
who are otherwise intelligent, have a high

00:38:27.680 --> 00:38:36.279
probability of being enumerate in that when
you present them with something like a statistical

00:38:36.279 --> 00:38:40.819
probability, even beyond just you know the
emotional impact of whatever is being talked

00:38:40.819 --> 00:38:47.260
about, death or debilitation, they are just
not able to understand the mathematics. They

00:38:47.260 --> 00:38:54.039
are not able to understand numbers, and What
are the best things that are being done right

00:38:54.039 --> 00:39:01.390
now in terms of medical information to present
those numbers in a way that is useful to the

00:39:01.390 --> 00:39:04.809
large percentage of people who don't really
see them as useful as numbers?

00:39:04.809 --> 00:39:10.220
Thomas Goetz &gt;&gt; Right, right. So one of the
